        <h2 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Ready to Switch?</h2>
        <p style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.9;">
          Install SuperLocalMemory V2 in 5 minutes. Free forever, 100% local, works everywhere.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/varun369/SuperLocalMemoryV2" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn" style="background: white; color: var(--color-accent);">
          ⭐ Star on GitHub & Get Started
